tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE inventory_management (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  item_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  quantity INT NOT NULL,
  category VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  last_replenished DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE seeds (seed_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
seed_name STRING,
quantity INT,
expiry_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE fertilizers (fertilizer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
fertilizer_name STRING,
quantity INT,
expiry_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE pesticides (pesticide_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
pesticide_name STRING,
quantity INT,
expiry_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE replenishment_history (replenishment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
item_id UUID,
item_type STRING,
replenishment_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    inventory_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    item_type VARCHAR(20),
    item_id INT,
    item_quantity INT,
    last_replenishment_date DATE
);
